#spchp.permission-guide .guide .microphone .sprite,
#spchp .close-button,
#spch .close-button,
#spch .spchc .microphone,
#spch .spchc .speaking .microphone {
    background-image: url(https://s.yimg.com/pv/static/img/voiceSearch1x-1620383531565.min.png);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: initial;
    color: transparent;
}
/* Retina displays */
@media
        only screen and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2),
        only screen and (min-device-pixel-ratio: 2),
        only screen and (min-resolution: 192dpi),
        only screen and (min-resolution: 2dppx) {
#spchp.permission-guide .guide .microphone .sprite,
#spchp .close-button,
#spch .close-button,
#spch .spchc .microphone,
#spch .spchc .speaking .microphone {
        background-size: 41px 330px;
        background-image: url(https://s.yimg.com/pv/static/img/voiceSearch2x-1620383531565.min.png)
}
    }

/* permission guide */
#spchp.permission-guide {
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
    background-color: #fff;
    left: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: fixed;
    text-align: left;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10000;
    transition: visibility 0s linear 0.218s, background-color 0.218s;
}
#spchp.permission-guide .close-button {
        background-position: 0 0;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        right: 0;
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 0;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        opacity: 0.8;
    }
#spchp.permission-guide .close-button:hover {
            opacity: 1;
        }
#spchp.permission-guide .guide {
        margin: 191px 0 0 507px;
    }
#spchp.permission-guide .guide .microphone {
            height: 68px;
            width: 52px;
            border-right: 1px solid #232a31;
            float: left;
        }
#spchp.permission-guide .guide .microphone .sprite {
                background-position: 0 -105px;
                width: 28px;
                height: 28px;
            }
#spchp.permission-guide .guide .guide-text {
            height: 68px;
            margin-left: 24px;
            float: left;
        }
#spchp.permission-guide .guide .guide-text .title {
                color: #232a31;
                font-size: 32px;
                font-family: HelveticaNeue-Bold;
                line-height: 28px;
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }
#spchp.permission-guide .guide .guide-text .text {
                color: #232a31;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 28px;
            }
#spchp.permission-guide.hide {
        display: none;
    }

/* speech panel */
#spch.spch {
    background: #fff;
    height: 100%;
    left: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: fixed;
    text-align: left;
    top: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 10000;
    transition: visibility 0s linear 0.218s, background-color 0.218s;
}
#spch.spch .close-button {
        background-position: 0 0;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        right: 0;
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 0;
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        opacity: 0.8;
    }
#spch.spch .close-button:hover {
            opacity: 1;
        }
#spch.spch .spchc {
        display: block;
        height: 97px;
        pointer-events: none;
    }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            opacity: 0.1;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.318s ease-in;
        }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .spch-control {
                display: inline-block;
            }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .text-container {
                float: left;
                height: 91px;
                overflow: hidden;
                margin: 3px 0;
                pointer-events: none;
                width: calc(50% - 48.5px);
            }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .text-container p {
                    display: table-cell;
                    vertical-align: middle;
                    width: 550px;
                    height: 97px;
                }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .text-container .spcht {
                    font-weight: normal;
                    color: #6e7780;
                    line-height: normal;
                    opacity: 0;
                    pointer-events: none;
                    text-align: left;
                    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
                    transition: opacity 0.1s ease-in, margin-left 0.5s ease-in, top 0s linear 0.218s;
                }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .text-container .spcht.hide {
                        display: none;
                    }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .text-container #spcht-retry {
                    color: #0f69ff;
                    cursor: pointer;
                    pointer-events: auto;
                }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container {
                pointer-events: none;
                position: relative;
                transition: transform 0.218s, opacity 0.218s ease-in;
            }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container .button {
                    background-color: #fff;
                    border: 1px solid #eee;
                    border-radius: 100%;
                    bottom: 0;
                    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                    cursor: pointer;
                    display: inline-block;
                    left: 0;
                    opacity: 0;
                    pointer-events: none;
                    position: absolute;
                    right: 0;
                    top: 0;
                    transition: background-color 0.218s, border 0.218s, box-shadow 0.218s;
                }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container .button .microphone {
                        background-position: 0 -24px;
                        width: 41px;
                        height: 41px;
                        left: 27px;
                        pointer-events: none;
                        position: absolute;
                        top: 27px;
                        transform: scale(1);
                    }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container.listening .ripple {
                        position: absolute;
                        width: 136px;
                        height: 136px;
                        z-index: -1;
                        left: 50%;
                        top: 50%;
                        opacity: 0;
                        margin: -70px 0 0 -70px;
                        border-radius: 100px;
                        -webkit-animation: ripple 3.3s infinite;
                                animation: ripple 3.3s infinite;
                        background-color: #fff !important;
                        border: 2px solid #e0e4e9;
                    }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container.listening .ripple:nth-child(2) {
                            -webkit-animation-delay: 1.1s;
                                    animation-delay: 1.1s;
                        }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container.listening .ripple:nth-child(3) {
                            -webkit-animation-delay: 2.2s;
                                    animation-delay: 2.2s;
                        }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container.speaking .button {
                        background-color: #0f69ff;
                    }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container.speaking .button .microphone {
                            background-position: 0 -65px;
                            width: 40px;
                            height: 40px;
                            pointer-events: none;
                            position: absolute;
                            transform: scale(1);
                        }
#spch.spch .spchc .inner-container .button-container.speaking .ripple {
                        background-size: 114px;
                        position: absolute;
                        width: 114px;
                        height: 114px;
                        z-index: -1;
                        left: 50%;
                        top: 50%;
                        margin: -57px 0 0 -57px;
                        -webkit-animation: speakingRipple1 2s infinite;
                                animation: speakingRipple1 2s infinite;
                    }
